description: This hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 432, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [432 Votes, Hall of Fame]
